snippet.title: Bigfoot : Collision Course (Nintendo DS 2008)
snippet.description:
Bigfoot : Collision Course is a 3D all-terrain vehicle racing game by Zoo Games.
If the bar at the bottom of the screen fills up, you can use power boost function to accelerate your vehicle more fast for 5 seconds.
The way to fill the boost bar is to obtain a green thunder item and to destroy objects.
